#: dashboard.js:928
msgid "During blocked hours the WiFi remains on — devices stay connected and keep their IP address. A firewall rule silently drops all internet traffic from the kids network. DNS still resolves and pings still work, so devices show as connected but cannot load pages or apps. Wired devices on the kids VLAN are affected in exactly the same way."
